```
upstream backend {
    server 127.0.0.1;
    keepalive 8;
}

server {
    listen 80;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://backend;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_set_header Connection "";
    }
}
```
如果把 www.abc.com 在 hosts 文件中解析为 127.0.0.1 ，然后
```
upstream backend {
    server www.abc.com;
    keepalive 8;
}

```
